  ('optometrist-moex-02134', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '眼球壁可分為三層，包括纖維層、血管層和神經層，下列何者不是位於血管層？', '["虹膜", "睫狀體", "脈絡膜", "視網膜"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "83b96228577e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b06aea28cc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0801", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-02135', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-108-b0a2f330', 'sub-optometrist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '人類眼球的血液供應主要來自於眼動脈，其在眼眶內的主要分支為中心視網膜動脈（central retinal artery） 和睫狀動脈（ciliary artery），下列視網膜各分層何者血液供應不是由中心視網膜動脈所供應？', '["外核層（outer nuclear layer）", "神經纖維層（nerve fiber layer）", "內核層（inner nuclear layer）", "神經節細胞層（ganglion cell layer）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "83b96228577e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e7b06aea28cc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "401", "s": "0801", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球解剖生理學與倫理法規", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
